data.description: You step inside, you'll be greeted by a large great room that is perfect for entertaining guests or simply relaxing with loved ones. The eat-in kitchen is a true highlight of this home, featuring 42" cabinets and stainless steel appliances, including a refrigerator. Whether you're a seasoned chef or just enjoy cooking, this kitchen will surely impress.    One of the standout features of this property is the indoor utility room, providing convenience and practicality. Additionally, this home boasts a 10x26 patio where you can unwind after a long day or host gatherings with friends and family.    Rest assured that this home has been meticulously maintained, ensuring that it is move-in ready for its new owners. The inclusion of blinds throughout adds an extra touch of privacy and comfort.    Located in a desirable neighborhood, this property offers easy access to amenities such as shopping centers, restaurants, and parks. Commuting will be a breeze with convenient transportation options nearby.    Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this beautiful home. Schedule a visit today to see all that 644 Gila Drive has to offer.
